  <brief_title>The Comparison Between Epidural and Intravenous Patient-controlled Analgesia for Laparoscopic Gastrectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Comparison Between Epidural and Intravenous Patient-controlled Analgesia for Laparoscopic Gastrectomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
